data.description: 100% Owner Financing - Bad Credit Accepted - on this lovely 4 bedrooms, 2 bath, 2 car garage Ranch style home. Situated on a 1 acre lot near Joint Base McGuire Fort Dix Lakehurst that features dinette and full living-room areas, hard wood floors, artesian well, whole house water filtration system, central air, finished basement with laundry room, Jacuzzi soaking tub, in-ground pool and Kuna WiFi security camera lights with 2-way communication and active motion.
